SUB_W04_EVAR_BOFO_BASE_SHIPYARD_010_CUT_.text:
You're a totally different person now;
you put that thing together faster
than I ever could have imagined.

SUB_W04_EVAR_BOFO_BASE_NORTHHARBOR_WORLD.text:
Baltasar's not a man to forget a grudge;
he's probably going to want to string
me up while he plays the hornpipe.

SUB_W04_EVAR_BOFO_BASE_WORLD_QUEST_LAST_.text:
The egg's responding to what he says;
I think that means we should keep it
far away from him.

SUB_W04_EVAR_BOFO_PIRATESHIP_BIGWAVE_KRA.text:
I know he be plannin' to wish
for some no-good thing,
but there be nothin' we can do.

SUB_W04_EVAR_BOFO_GHOSTSHIP_DEATH_COVE_1.text:
Deus Maris asked us to do this;
he wants us to take these things
outta the world for him.

SUB_W04_EVAR_BOFO_GHOSTSHIP_LASTBATTLE_1.text:
Ah. It seems the wish comes with a price;
I cannot be freed from my burden until I
bring down this fiend.
